### =============================================================================
### smoke-tests.http  -  Manual smoke tests (VS Code "REST Client" extension).
### Replace the @variables below, then click "Send Request" above each call.
###
### How to get values:
###   @gateway : az apim show -g <rg> -n <apim> --query gatewayUrl -o tsv
###   @apiKey  : az rest --method post \
###              --url "https://management.azure.com/subscriptions/<sub>/resourceGroups/<rg>/providers/Microsoft.ApiManagement/service/<apim>/subscriptions/p1subscriptionteam1/listSecrets?api-version=2024-05-01" \
###              --query primaryKey -o tsv
### =============================================================================

@gateway = https://<apim-name>.azure-api.net
@apiKey = <subscription-primary-key>
@apiVersion = 2024-10-21

### GPT-5 Nano - chat completion
POST {{gateway}}/gpt5-nano/deployments/gpt-5-nano/chat/completions?api-version={{apiVersion}}
api-key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messages": [{ "role": "user", "content": "Reply with the single word: pong." }],
  "max_tokens": 16
}

### GPT-5 Mini - chat completion
POST {{gateway}}/gpt5-mini/deployments/gpt-5-mini/chat/completions?api-version={{apiVersion}}
api-key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messages": [{ "role": "user", "content": "Say hi." }],
  "max_tokens": 16
}

