### Embeddings - text-embedding-3-large
POST {{gateway}}/embeddings/deployments/text-embedding-3-large/embeddings?api-version={{apiVersion}}
api-key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "input": "hello world"
}

### Streaming chat (validates forced stream_options.include_usage for token accounting)
POST {{gateway}}/gpt5-nano/deployments/gpt-5-nano/chat/completions?api-version={{apiVersion}}
api-key: {{apiKey}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messages": [{ "role": "user", "content": "Count to three." }],
  "max_tokens": 32,
  "stream": true
}

### Negative test - missing api-key should return 401
POST {{gateway}}/gpt5-nano/deployments/gpt-5-nano/chat/completions?api-version={{apiVersion}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "messages": [{ "role": "user", "content": "should fail" }],
  "max_tokens": 8
}
